      'dn.lede': 'Connect with a <strong>certified Macedonian notary</strong> via video call and finish notarization <strong>in 15 minutes</strong> — without leaving home. Result: <strong>legally valid electronic document</strong> with full legal weight per ZEDEIDU and eIDAS Regulation EU 910/2014.',
